  "description": "<p>Lighter and brighter than its non-CORE sibling, Petzl\u2019s Actik CORE is here to illuminate your adventures. The narrow and wide beams can be used on their own or together, great for running in low light. The easy to recharge CORE battery pack takes away the need to keep batteries on hand. And with up to 600 lumens and reflective details on the strap, you will see and be seen.</p><ul><li>5 modes, 3 in white light: high (2h at 600 lumens), medium (7h at 100 lumens), low (100h at 7 lumens), 2 in red: continuous (60h at 2 lumens) and strobe (400h at 2 lumens). Runtimes from use with CORE battery, runtimes will differ with 3 AAA batteries</li><li>Wide and narrow beams provide the right light for nearly any activity</li><li>Red LED is great for preserving night vision and not disturbing tent mates</li><li>CORE USB rechargeable battery pack makes it easy to keep your light topped up and ready to go</li><li>Compatible with 3 x AAA batteries if you find yourself away from a USB port</li><li>IPX4 water proofing keeps the light keeps shining even when Mother Nature has other ideas</li><li>Centre-mounted pivot lets you aim the light up or down</li><li>Glow in the dark reflector ring helps you find your light in the dark</li><li>Reflective detailing on the headband helps keep you seen</li><li>Updated strap uses a dual sliding buckle system that is faster and easier to adjust than previous generations</li><li>Lockout mode prevents light from being switched on inside your pack</li><li>Included white storage pouch doubles as a light diffusing lantern</li></ul>",
